# Root-level local reports. The public-source manifest and CI test remain the
# authoritative allowlist even when a filename does not match these patterns.
/*[Rr][Ee][Ff][Ee][Rr][Ee][Nn][Cc][Ee]_[Aa][Nn][Aa][Ll][Yy][Ss][Ii][Ss]*
/*[Ee][Cc][Oo][Ss][Yy][Ss][Tt][Ee][Mm]_[Rr][Ee][Ss][Ee][Aa][Rr][Cc][Hh]*
/*[Rr][Ee][Ss][Ee][Aa][Rr][Cc][Hh]_[Nn][Oo][Tt][Ee][Ss]*
/*[Rr][Ee][Vv][Ee][Rr][Ss][Ee]_[Rr][Ee][Pp][Oo][Rr][Tt]*
/*[Pp][Rr][Ii][Vv][Aa][Tt][Ee]_[Nn][Oo][Tt][Ee][Ss]*
/*[Ii][Nn][Tt][Ee][Rr][Nn][Aa][Ll]_[Nn][Oo][Tt][Ee][Ss]*
/*[Aa][Uu][Dd][Ii][Tt]*
/*[Cc][Hh][Ee][Cc][Kk][Pp][Oo][Ii][Nn][Tt]*
/*[Aa][Cc][Cc][Ee][Pp][Tt][Aa][Nn][Cc][Ee]*
/*[Ee][Vv][Ii][Dd][Ee][Nn][Cc][Ee]*
